<i>noun</i>: 정열 [정녈], 욕정 [욕쩡], 열정 [열쩡], 수난 [수난], 기 [기], 격정 [격쩡] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정열 [정녈]</dt><br>
<dd>passion</dd><br>
<dd>마음속에서 뜨겁고 강하게 일어나는 적극적인 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>A spontaneous feeling that arises intensely and strongly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>욕정 [욕쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>1. desire; passion</dd><br>
<dd>순간적으로 생겨나는, 무엇을 바라거나 원하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>An instant surge of desire to hope for or want something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sexual desire; lust</dd><br>
<dd>이성에 대한 육체적인 욕망.</dd><br>
<dd>The desire to have sexual intercourse with the opposite sex.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>열정 [열쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>passion</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 뜨거운 애정을 가지고 열심히 하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of doing something hard with enthusiasm.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>수난 [수난]</dt><br>
<dd>1. suffering; ordeal</dd><br>
<dd>견디기 힘든 어려운 일을 당함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of suffering an unbearable experience.</dd><br>
<dd>2. Passion</dd><br>
<dd>기독교에서, 예수가 십자가에 못 박힐 때 당한 고난.</dd><br>
<dd>In Christianity, the suffering faced by Jesus Christ when he was crucified.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>기 [기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spirit; energy</dd><br>
<dd>활동의 바탕이 되는 힘.</dd><br>
<dd>The force that acts as the basis for doing something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. enthusiasm; passion</dd><br>
<dd>몸 안에 있는 정신적인 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>Mental power existing in one's body.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>격정 [격쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>passion</dd><br>
<dd>강렬하고 갑자기 생기는 참기 어려운 감정.</dd><br>
<dd>A powerful, sudden burst of uncontrollable emotion.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>